    <title><literal>NoCDR()</literal></title>

    <indexterm significance="preferred">
      <primary>Dialplan Applications</primary>

      <secondary><code>NoCDR()</code></secondary>
    </indexterm>

    <simpara>Suppresses generation of a Call Detail Record for the call on the
    current channel.</simpara>

    <synopsis><command>NoCDR()</command></synopsis>

    <simpara>Suppresses generation of a CDR for the current call.</simpara>

    <programlisting>; no CDR for calls to INWATS directory assistance:
exten =&gt; 18005551212,1,Answer()
exten =&gt; 18005551212,n,NoCDR()
exten =&gt; 18005551212,n,Dial(Zap/4/18005551212)</programlisting>

